Interface QueryBuilder<Q extends Query>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    FilterConditionBeginContext

    public interface QueryBuilder<Q extends Query>
extends FilterConditionBeginContext
    A builder for Query objects. An instance of this class can be obtained from QueryFactory.

    Type parameter Q will be removed in Infinispan 9.0
